{"tid":586300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人教我點處理?","createTime":"2018-03-09T11:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T12:48:28.000Z","uid":155005,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4aef2c593c64935224bcd22c13e00298982187b3","tid":586300,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"琴晚林收鋪 有條女黎買電話！左住我收工<br />\n一開波竟然唔係問我有咩款好介紹<br />\n而係問我用咩型號電話<br />\n<br />\n我答佢：iPhone X<br />\n佢就話：咁我要部iPhone SE<br />\n<br />\n我心諗：呢個系客 95搭8！<br />\n<br />\n之後我循列比佢cheak完 埋單就趕佢走<br />\n佢竟然話要埋做會員 咁我唯有拿拿聲比佢填張form趕佢扯喇<br />\n<br />\n係佢林走既時候 佢叫我拎部電話出黎<br />\n佢將岩岩買既IPhone SE 拼落 我部IPhone X度<br />\n佢面都紅曬話：明唔明呀？<br />\n跟手佢收返部電話再將岩岩填完既會員form比返我 就急急腳咁走<br />\n我留意到張form佢剩係填左 （個人地址）果一列<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪比暗示我？ 因為IPhone SE + IPhone X=SEX<br />\n再加埋一張只有佢地址既form比我"},{"pid":"e3e93697f8d5c327b7a699efe2d1985052292d51","tid":586300,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5579d796105fbd5d703a1f8702db6daea53e28b","tid":586300,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf4a26ef8a6c4105708f011e03ae1ce9d5cf801","tid":586300,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"系？"},{"pid":"2dc472eba84818823f45dac9d504061b476898e2","tid":586300,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"有病去睇下醫生好d"},{"pid":"bd9f841cecaa117982ef5a054d7dcc13f22b3c73","tid":586300,"uid":150935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca84539ef4c7b181f29a92d12d712c98f044a3be","tid":586300,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0